description: Try our easy to follow Prawn Gyoza Soup recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
name: Prawn Gyoza Soup Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Stir in bok choy and half the spring onion and cook for 1-2 minutes, or until wilted. Divide soup among bowls and top with remaining spring onion and chilli, if using. Note: Use chicken or fish stock in place of the soup base, if you prefer.
